# 🌱 PlantCare

**PlantCare** is an intelligent plant management web app that empowers users to identify, track, and care for their plants effortlessly. By simply uploading a plant image, users can receive AI-powered predictions including the **plant name**, **ideal watering frequency**, **sunlight type**, and **temperature range** — all organized beautifully in personalized plant cards. 🌼

---

## 🌟 Key Features

* 🔐 **User Authentication**

  * Secure login to manage your plant collection.

* 📷 **Image-Based Plant Recognition**

  * Upload a photo and let the AI suggest plant details instantly.

* 🧠 **Smart Predictions via API**

  * Identify:

    * ✅ Plant Name
    * 💧 Watering Schedule
    * ☀️ Sunlight Requirement
    * 🌡️ Temperature Range

* 🪴 **My Plants Dashboard**

  * Store and view all your saved plants with details in custom **Plant Cards**.

* ⏰ **Reminders**

  * Add watering or replanting reminders to each plant.

* 💻 **Responsive Design**

  * Optimized for desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer      | Technology                                                      |
| ---------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Frontend   | **React**, Tailwind CSS / Material UI                           |
| API        | **Plant Identification API** (e.g., Plant.id / Custom AI Model) |
| Auth       | Supabase auth                                                   |
| Database   | Supabase db                                                     |
| Deployment | Vercel / Netlify (optional)                                     |

---

---

## 📦 Installation & Setup

To run this project locally:

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/plantcare.git
cd plantcare

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the development server
npm start
```
